article_title: Counseling events help people find health insurance
article_text:
Tuesday is the deadline to enroll in a healthcare plan to have coverage by Jan. 1

Those without health insurance by Jan. 31 face a fine under the Affordable Care Act

Free help in finding an affordable plan is available

article_metadata.title: Counseling events help people find health insurance | News & Observer

og.description: Antonyo Thompson, a dump truck driver, struggled to find affordable health insurance for himself and his spouse.
